Achievements.Name: Let Me Out!
Achievements.Description: Rescue a friendly hero from a cage.

Achievements.Name: A Helping Hand
Achievements.Description: Complete any of the mini side-quests given by an NPC in a level.

Achievements.Name: It Wasn't Me!
Achievements.Description: Defeat 9 enemies in a level while remaining in Pacifist Mode.

Achievements.Name: The Artful Dodger
Achievements.Description: Complete a level without triggering any alarms.

Achievements.Name: One Hand Tied Behind My Back
Achievements.Description: Complete a level without using any Skills or Powers.

Achievements.Name: I Love Treasure!
Achievements.Description: Open a total of 20 Treasure Chests in a single game.

Achievements.Name: Peace and Non Violence
Achievements.Description: Collect 12 Pacifist Orbs in a level.

Achievements.Name: We Don't Need Roads!
Achievements.Description: Complete a game in without using the Teleportation Shrine.

Achievements.Name: Weapon Unlocked: Bone Dagger!
Achievements.Description: Complete at least 3 levels in Pacifist mode to unlock the Bone Dagger!

Achievements.Name: Weapon Unlocked: Musket Gun!
Achievements.Description: Achieve a score of 25,000 in New Game Plus to unlock the Musket Gun!

Achievements.Name: Weapon Unlocked: Infinity Sword!
Achievements.Description: Complete the game 3 times to unlock the Infinity Sword!
